channel.title: iQuality - Final release
channel.description:
[CENTER]Hello I decided to release this due I see no motivation/enjoyment in RSPS anymore. You should all take this as a game, not as a income for money. Take it or leave it and I wish you all the best of luck with your Server's. I don't give a shit about it anymore and I am quiting RSPS for good.
Feel free to thank, would not give a shit about that too ;)

item.title: iQuality - Final release
item.dc:creator: @Xx_Weed_Xx Xx Weed Xx
item.description:
@Xx_Weed_Xx wrote:

Fixes for people who wish to use this as a base.

Q. Client no connecting?
A. Change the IP address to localhost in client.java (client side).

Q. Compiler not working?
A. If you get system path error then you need to find your Java version and replace it.

If you’ve done and it still doesn’t work replace your compiler with this:

@echo off title Jeff's compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.7.0_02\bin\javac.exe" -classpath deps/log4j-1.2.15.jar;deps/jython.jar;deps/xstream.jar;deps/mina.jar;deps/mysql.jar;deps/poi.jar;deps/slf4j.jar;deps/slf4j-nop.jar -d bin src\rs2\model\players\content\Teleporting\*.java src\rs2\model\players\content\bankPin\*.java src\rs2\model\players\content\Barrows\*.java src\rs2\model\players\content\ClanWars\*.java src\rs2\model\players\content\minigames\*.java src\rs2\model\players\content\PartyRoom\*.java src\rs2\model\players\content\PestControl\*.java src\rs2\model\players\content\randomevents\*.java src\rs2\model\players\content\summoning\*.java src\rs2\model\players\content\WarriorGuild\*.java src\rs2\model\combat\*.java src\rs2\model\players\content\randomevents\*.java src\rs2\event\*.java src\rs2\model\items\*.java src\rs2\model\npcs\*.java src\rs2\model\objects\*.java src\rs2\model\players\content\bankpin\*.java src\rs2\model\players\content\*.java src\rs2\model\players\skills\*.java src\rs2\model\players\*.java src\rs2\model\players\packets\*.java src\rs2\model\shops\*.java src\rs2\net\*.java src\rs2\task\*.java src\rs2\util\*.java src\rs2\world\*.java src\rs2\util\log\*.java src\rs2\*.java src\rs2\world\map\*.java pause

Q. Error loading 5, 4, 3, 2, 1.
A. Change where the cache goes in signlink.

If you can’t work it out with the information I gave you above then you don’t deserve to use this source, I think I’ve spoon fed too much already.

Read full topic
